      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm even typing this. everything just... it all fell apart today. the grant was rejected and my advisor basically told me there's no path forward for the project. years of my life, just gone. i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this lab. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. i just want everything to stop. i just want some kind of peace that doesn't involve more \"trying.\"",
