      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the grant though. it's like the exhaustion is in my bones. i look at the people around me and everyone is just constantly pushing, constantly striving, and i just don't have it in me anymore. it feels like i've been running a marathon for years and i just hit a wall that i can't climb over. everything feels so heavy and pointless. i just want to sleep and never have to face another deadline or another failure ever again. i just want the noise to go quiet.",
